org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.dictionary

Class RareWordTermMapCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.dictionary.RareWordTermMapCreator

  • public final class RareWordTermMapCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a collection of RareWordTermMapCreator.CuiTerm Objects, this factory can create a Map of RareWordTerm collections indexed by rare word. This map can be used to create a MemRareWordDictionary
